ra, smartphone or other device is quite easy with Sony Movie Platinum Suite. The importation feature works well with almost every file type and codec we look for when we rate and rank the best DVD authoring software. In fact, there are only two kinds of files that this DVD maker doesn&#39;t work with â€“ WMV HD and DivX.","The non-linear editing portion of Sony Movie Studio Platinum Suite 12 features an intuitive drag-and-drop interface. This makes it easy to find the footage you want, drop it on the timeline, and then place audio, images, transitions and effects around it to create the experience you want for your audience. This DVD creator features more than 200 transitions and 350 effects for you to choose from.","When you&#39;ve completed the process of editing your project, Sony Movie Studio Platinum Suite employs DVD Architect Studio to do the actual DVD authoring. This application walks you through creating menus, chapter breaks and special features. You may spend a few hours getting it right, but it is well worth the time it takes to learn to use this application to its full potential."]},"id":"60bd037a-f210-45a8-b403-cf6419a5ba96","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"ad6e2843-07da-47ce-9262-39cef380d15f","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["While Sony Movie Studio Platinum Suite 12 doesn&#39;t have the power of professional video editing software, it has all the features the pros use to enable you to create beautiful video projects you will be proud of. The simplicity of the interface and the DVD menu creator applications are the high points of this DVD authoring software."]},"id":"5b821fcc-7ec4-4ec2-9224-8bab3b006a0c","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_57081","url":"/sony-movie-studio-platinum-suite-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"j-d-chadwick","url":"/author/j-d-chadwick","dateCreated":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","name":"J.D. Chadwick","dateModified":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","id":"Q2hDFnLxcyQrSWYJF8ZLKH","dateImpo